data.description: This beautiful sprawling ranch features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and oversized 2.5-car garage! Spacious living room with wall of windows overlooking private backyard with wood burning fireplace and vaulted beamed ceiling. Eat-in kitchen with new white cabinets, granite countertops and brand new stainless steel hood and fridge. Family room has vaulted beam ceiling and sliding patio door leading out to 4-season porch. Down the hall are three large bedrooms with plenty of closet space. Fourth bedroom would make a great flex room and can easily be an office or playroom as well. Two remodeled bathrooms with walk-in showers. Finished basement with new flooring, wet bar and half bathroom. Sitting on over half an acre with a circle drive and mature trees in a park-like setting.
